column7: Today, I felt that I’m nothing. Compared to others, I’m just a nobody. I’m a mere tool for their convenience. My opinions are not valued nor considered. I felt so sad today that I cried when the sad music was played. However, after talking to my friend, some sadness was released. However, since I was a child, I hold grudges, unknowingly I carry it up to today. Not knowing what to do, I just go with the flow. #SuperLost #SadMusic #Notmyday

Today, I was so tired. I went home. Thankfully, my dad went to pick me up. Listening to old songs in the car was so much fun. I think it was one of my favorite bonding time with my dad. :smiling_face_with_open_mouth: #SuperFun #IllAlwaysRemember #DadAndMe

Today, I cried a lot. My mom told me that I have an attitude problem. I felt sad. I was always depressed to the thought that all my opinions don’t matter. I have a wall that no one can go through. My mom told me to change , for me to understand others. In that way, I can fully accept a person in the future. :sad_face: #Cried
Today, was kinda tiring. I was disappointed with some people because of their actions. They don’t know how to respect others :disappointed_face:

Today, I felt bitter. I greeted my friend late for her birthday. I was still contemplating whether to greet her since she didn’t greet me either last month. But then she purposely told other people who didn’t greet her are kind of… Regretting, I still greeted her in our chatroom. I never got a reply, I was seen zoned. Why does my kindness never go back on me! I’m so tired of being good and understanding! T_T T_T #Why?? #ImsoPissed

Today, it was tiring. I was so sleepy I cannot concentrate on my lesson. I shouldn’t have stayed late yesterday night. :pensive_face: #SleepIsAllINeed Sleep is love. We should all be sleeping properly. I hope I can do that always.

Today, I laughed out loud. My classmates are super funny. They keep joking during our break. When I went back to my dorm, my roommates created a tour video inside our tiny room. Today was super funny. I hope to laugh only in the next days. Amen! :smiling_face_with_open_mouth: #HeyHeyHey #FunFunFun
Today was a stressful day. I was very confused from all the lectures we had. I felt gloomy until I watched my favorite show. Indeed, me time is a happy time. :smiling_face: #ILoveMeTime

Today, I was so relieved that it’s Saturday. My friends and I was so hyper we even chased our professor. :smiling_face: We were all inside the elevator. Our professor has this rule that whoever comes  late after him would be considered late in his class.
My aunt celebrated her birthday today since it’s a long time we all gathered in one place. It’s nice to see all of them, it brings joy and peace within me. #Family

Today was rest day. :smiling_face_with_open_mouth: I finally got to sleep for a very long time. I was quite on the verge of crying since my sister is sick. :sad_face: I will be forced to go to our dorm earlier as planned. But then as an older sibling, it’s my job #Duties

I woke up late today. I studied late and still wasn’t able to finish. I’m sick. :sad_face: I think I got it from my sister. :sad_face: #Fluvirus I hate it when I have flu. I should’ve been more careful than anyone.

Bobby released a music video today!!! :smiling_face_with_heart_shaped_eyes: :smiling_face_with_heart_shaped_eyes: :smiling_face_with_heart_shaped_eyes: His mv was lit :smiling_face_with_smiling_eyes: :smiling_face_with_smiling_eyes: :smiling_face_with_smiling_eyes: the background was making me dizzy because of the familiar codes though :face_with_tears_of_joy: :face_with_tears_of_joy: :face_with_tears_of_joy: #Bobby #iKON #Holup #MOBB

Wow!!! Donghae and Siwon recorded a music video while having police duties :face_with_tears_of_joy: :face_with_tears_of_joy: :face_with_tears_of_joy: I miss super junior :crying_face: :crying_face:  :crying_face:  :crying_face: :loudly_crying_face: :loudly_crying_face: :loudly_crying_face: :loudly_crying_face: :loudly_crying_face: #SuperJunior #WatchOut
I was super sleepy during our class. We have a three  hour lecture but on the third hour, my professor words were just entering yet leaving my ears hahaha  :loudly_crying_face:  #sleepyday
Today is my favorite day. Our class is just for 3 hours plus 1 hour break. Super lazy today hehe #FeelingLight #MyDay

Listening to music while reviewing. But not really reviewing because I’m just singing along with the music. OPM, Kpop, English songs. Whatever song comes on; I just sing along. Not even reviewing. :face_with_tears_of_joy: #ICS132

Actually, I can’t really review well. Many things roam my mind today. I’m very worried about academic-related things. Quizzes. Exams. Thesis. Thesis. Thesis. Thesis. There’s progress, but I don’t think it’s enough. Why am I not motivated?? Why am I not pressured?? I want to do things for the thesis, but I’m always just sleeping. Or thinking about things not related to thesis. I need to find the reason again why I’m doing this, why I am here in the first place. What am I even doing here? I need to find a reason. Please give me a reason. Just give me a reason. :smiling_face_with_open_mouth: :smiling_face_with_open_mouth: :smiling_face_with_open_mouth: Random thoughts pop in my mind today. I suddenly missed my high school classmates. :face_with_tears_of_joy: What are they doing these days? I think the last time I talked to more than 5 high school classmates was years ago. :face_with_tears_of_joy: :face_with_tears_of_joy: :crying_face: :crying_face: :loudly_crying_face: :loudly_crying_face:

I’m working on this chaptered story about us friends. :smiling_face_with_open_mouth:. And I completed one chapter with 2428 words! It’s a first time for me to write a chaptered story with one chapter with 2000+ words! It’s a love story, btw. It’s actually Micah-centric like the whole story will revolve around my love life (which actually exists in this story, not in real life) but every chapter will be a story about my friends’ love lives. Hehe. Hope this turns out well! Fighting! :grinning_face_with_smiling_eyes: :grinning_face_with_smiling_eyes: :grinning_face_with_smiling_eyes: :smiling_face_with_halo: :smiling_face_with_halo: :smiling_face_with_halo: #untitled
Today I was super nervous because we had a quiz. I slept while studying for that quiz.  :smiling_face_with_halo: Thankfully I was able to go through it :smiling_face_with_halo:  #SuperLucky

It was kind of a waste to throw away the good ideas we have for the story. I’m a little fazed by the fact that I am writing a story about me and my friend’s brother. So, I decided to stop writing things that will end up with our story, instead, we’re finding for alternatives. My mood kinda went down so I’m not going to write anything for the story again today. I’ll be resting and change my mood for tomorrow. #untitled

I’m overwhelmed by my friends’ appreciation for my story. :face_with_tears_of_joy: :face_with_tears_of_joy: It feels good to have someone to share my imaginations with. :grinning_face_with_smiling_eyes: :grinning_face_with_smiling_eyes: :grinning_face_with_smiling_eyes: #untitled

Today, I went home and my dad was waiting for me. When I saw our car, I run to it but when I got there I was quite flustered.  :smiling_face_with_halo: There was a man in the front and back seat and then I thought, "Is this our car" but then I saw my dad in the driver seat. Those people were just his officemates. I was quite scared for nothing  :face_with_tears_of_joy: #ScaredForNothing
I was doing my assignment for one whole day. However, I still can't find the right answer. I was on the verge of crying but then my friends came to the rescue.  hushed_face  #IFeelSoBlessed

Can’t really sleep on ‘normal’ times. I can only sleep when it’s in the wee hours of the morning. I think it’s good for me? Because I’m productive during dawn. But I’m getting sick when sleeping late………
Just finished watching Train to Busan. So many feels.  :face_screaming_in_fear: :face_screaming_in_fear: :face_screaming_in_fear: #TrainToBusan
I'm preparing for a report today. I still don't know what to do. I'm super confused huhu :loudly_crying_face: #LordHelp

My left arm feel so numb. I got a vaccine today. It hurts all day. My parents were very proud that I can handle things like these myself. :heavy_black_heart: I feel so happy to hear those words everytime. #IFeelSoProud
